node.title: Murder of Pennsylvania teacher remains unsolved
node.description: The case of Rachael DelTondo, of a young teacher killed steps from her home, is still unsolved over three years later,. A person of interest in her murder was convicted in another homicide.
node.content: ["The case of a young teacher killed steps from her home, is still unsolved over three years later. A person of interest in her murder was convicted in another homicide. \"48 Hours\" has the latest in the case \"Who Killed Rachael DelTondo,\" airing Saturday, December 11 on CBS and Paramount+", "Rachael DelTondo was 33 years old when she was killed in 2018. Her murder is still unsolved today, but Beaver County District Attorney David Lozier says the investigation is active."]
